Bixby to his wife, Debby Bixby, dated July 9, 1933 on stationery from The Bridge House Hotel in Nanking [Nanjing]; includes description of the city of Nanjing and negotiations with the minister of communications [Chu Chia-hua], Dai [Enki], and [K.C.] Huang.
